scene.message:
Mark: All right, {ctl0f:1}.{nl}
Let's try setting the{nl}
'Half Compact' on the stand.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:60}No,{nl}
it's nothing.{nl}
Go on.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You're acting weird.{nl}
You're strange enough already.{waitkey}You've been like this{nl}
this whole time.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1},{nl}
Kandori and Aki are{nl}
just above us...{waitkey}We've finally made it{nl}
this far.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Oh no!{nl}
We have to get Mai's{nl}
compact back!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hurry up.{nl}
You just gotta set the{nl}
compact on that stand.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Damn it!{nl}
We fell right{nl}
into his trap.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Either way, we had{nl}
no choice but to dance{nl}
to his tune...{waitkey}Underhanded, but a{nl}
clever way to do it.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:60}Kandori...{nl}
I won't let you escape.{nl}
I'll settle this grudge.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...{nl}
I have a bad feeling.{nl}
Be careful, {ctl07:1}.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I knew it... But{nl}
nothing's happened to{nl}
you, {ctl07:1}, so{waitkey}I'm relieved.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: That's dirty!{nl}
Is this even allowed?!{nl}
Man, I'm seriously ticked off!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: No fair!{nl}
Using people is the{nl}
absolute worst!{waitkey}Guys like that are the{nl}
most infuriating ever!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What Kandori wanted{nl}
was that compact.{nl}
If he couldn't touch Mai...{waitkey}{clearbox}he'd just have someone{nl}
else bring it. We were{nl}
used as his pawns.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Say what?!{nl}
That bastard!!{nl}
You knew? You should've{nl}
told us!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: But why?{nl}
He could've just taken the{nl}
compact. Why bring us in?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: He's telling us{nl}
to come. He must be{nl}
awfully confident.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Looking down on us...{nl}
Fine, I'll play along!{nl}
Let's go, {ctl0f:1}!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: The haunted manor...{nl}
I used to sneak in a lot{nl}
as a kid...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Huh... who was it...{waitkey}who saved me back then...?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...No, that's wrong.{nl}
But if I think of it{nl}
this way... no, wait...{waitkey}Hm? I'm busy right now.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1},{nl}
let's hurry to the{nl}
haunted house!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: The haunted manor's{nl}
to the south of here,{nl}
right?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hurry, hurry!{nl}
No time to dawdle, right?!{nl}
The manor's to the south?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Is this the time{nl}
for chitchat?!{nl}
Hurry and chase him!{waitkey}{ret}
